0 \le \dfrac{7\pi}{8} \le \pi
\cos \dfrac \pi 8= - \cos \dfrac{7\pi}8
\cos \theta = \frac{(A,B)}{||A||\,||B||}
 \cos \phi = \frac{(B,C)}{||B||\, ||C||} = - \frac{(A,B)}{||B||\, ||C||} = - \cos \frac \pi 8.
\phi = \cos^{-1} \left( - \cos \frac \pi 8 \right)=\cos^{-1} \left( \cos \frac{7\pi}{8} \right) = \frac{7\pi}{8}.
